  "texts": [
    "Our watermark affects column-wise quantities as follows:1.",
    "For each column j, the column mean is preserved:1 N N i=1 ∆x i,j = 0.",
    "2.Pearson correlation coefficients (PCC).",
    "Let r jℓ and r wm jℓ be the PCCs between columns j and ℓ before and after watermarking, respectively.",
    "Define ∆r jℓ:= r wm jℓ -r jℓ."
